This repo contains DFModel to model DL performance on modern accelerators.

How to use:
1. Set up your csv file for in a folder in the current directory (name the folder after the DL model name).
2. Run "protoc --python_out=. setup.proto" to generate protobuf file (setup_pb2.py).
3. Run "python parse_csv.py --name=your_model_name" to generate protobuf binary (DSE.pb) and text file in that folder (DSE.txt).
4. Run "python visualize_dataflow_graph.py --name=your_model_name" to generate pydot graph file in that folder (your_model_name.png).

